      <item>
        <title>5 Common Words</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;!-- _includes/base.html --&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;write-a-test-that-generates-5-common-words-test-by-word&quot;&gt;1) Write a test that generates 5 common words (test-by-word)&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hint:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;Enter the following into a text file called five-common-words.rb&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You will be tested against the  words on a word-by-word basis (rather than letter-by-letter):&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;# five-common-words.rb&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;require&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;cw&#39;&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nf&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;do&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;comment&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;5 common words at 12 words per minute&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;shuffle&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;word_count&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;wpm&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;12&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(download: &lt;a href=&quot;../assets/rb/five-common-words.rb&quot;&gt;five-common-words.rb&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;output&quot;&gt;Output:&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;hr /&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;../assets/images/five-common-words.png&quot; alt=&quot;5 common words&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;hr /&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hint:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;The words in red were entered incorrectly!&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;write-a-test-that-generates-5-common-words-test-by-letter&quot;&gt;2) Write a test that generates 5 common words (test-by-letter)&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Instead of  testing &lt;i&gt;word-by-word&lt;/i&gt;, you may  also test &lt;i&gt;letter-by-letter&lt;/i&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hint:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;You should find this more informative if you are guessing some letters incorrectly&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;# five-common-words-2.rb&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;require&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;cw&#39;&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nf&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;do&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;comment&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;5 common words at 12 words per minute&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;shuffle&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;wpm&lt;/span&gt;        &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;12&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;word_count&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;test_letters&lt;/span&gt;    &lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;# notice we have added the command test_letters&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(download: &lt;a href=&quot;../assets/rb/five-common-words-2.rb&quot;&gt;five-common-words-2.rb&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;output-1&quot;&gt;Output:&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hint:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;The letters in red are were entered incorrectly!&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;hr /&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;../assets/images/five-common-words-2.png&quot; alt=&quot;5 common words 2&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;hr /&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;combine-both-examples-into-a-single-test&quot;&gt;3) Combine both examples into a single test&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;# five-common-words-3.rb&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;require&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;cw&#39;&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nf&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;do&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;comment&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;5 common words at 12 wpm (test letters)&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;shuffle&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;wpm&lt;/span&gt;        &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;12&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;word_count&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;test_letters&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nf&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;do&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;comment&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;5 common words at 12 wpm (test words)&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;shuffle&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;wpm&lt;/span&gt;        &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;12&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;word_count&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(download: &lt;a href=&quot;../assets/rb/five-common-words-3.rb&quot;&gt;five-common-words-3.rb&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;five-common-words-repeat-until-correct&quot;&gt;4) Five common words (repeat until correct)&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;hint:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;using the&lt;/em&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;repeat_word&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;command repeats the word until it is entered correctly&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;# five-common-words-4.rb&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;require&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;cw&#39;&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nf&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;do&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;comment&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;5 common words at 12 wpm (test letters)&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;shuffle&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;wpm&lt;/span&gt;        &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;12&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;word_count&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;repeat_word&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(download: &lt;a href=&quot;../assets/rb/five-common-words-4.rb&quot;&gt;five-common-words-4.rb&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;create-the-bare-minimum-example-below-and-see-what-happens&quot;&gt;5) Create the bare minimum example below and see what happens:&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;hint:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;to quit any test hit the q key four times successively&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;# five-common-words-5.rb&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;require&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;cw&#39;&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nf&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;do&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(download: &lt;a href=&quot;../assets/rb/five-common-words-5.rb&quot;&gt;five-common-words-5.rb&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;hint:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;default values are used for word_count and wpm - and since shuffle is not used, the same words will be used on subsequent runs&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tut/words-of-fixed-length.html&quot;&gt;Next - Words of Fixed Length&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

</description>
