      <item>
        <title>Words of Fixed Length</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;!-- _includes/base.html --&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;write-a-test-that-generates-5-words-of-4-characters-test-by-letter&quot;&gt;1) Write a test that generates 5 words of 4 characters (test-by-letter)&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;# five-words-five-letters.rb&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;require&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;cw&#39;&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nf&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;do&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;comment&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;5 words having 4 letters (12 WPM)&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;shuffle&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;word_count&lt;/span&gt;    &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;word_length&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;wpm&lt;/span&gt;           &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;12&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;test_letters&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(download: &lt;a href=&quot;../assets/rb/five-words-five-letters.rb&quot;&gt;five-words-five-letters.rb&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;write-a-test-that-generates-4-words-of-6-characters&quot;&gt;2) Write a test that generates 4 words of 6 characters&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;# five-words-five-letters.rb&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;require&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;cw&#39;&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nf&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;do&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;comment&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;4 words having 6 letters (15 WPM)&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;shuffle&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;wpm&lt;/span&gt;                 &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;15&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;number_of_words&lt;/span&gt;     &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;# you can use number_of_words or word_count&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;word_having_size_of&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;# you can use word_having_size_of or word_length&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(download: &lt;a href=&quot;../assets/rb/four-words-six-letters.rb&quot;&gt;four-words-six-letters.rb&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tut/words-with-length-variation.html&quot;&gt;Next - Words with Length Variation&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

</description>
