      <item>
        <title>Words with Length Variation</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;!-- _includes/base.html --&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;write-a-test-that-generates-8-words-of-length-5-or-less-characters&quot;&gt;1) Write a test that generates 8 words of length 5 or less characters&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;# eight-words-five-or-less-letters.rb&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;require&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;cw&#39;&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nf&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;do&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;comment&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;Eight words, five or less letters (18 WPM)&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;shuffle&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;no_longer_than&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;word_count&lt;/span&gt;     &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;8&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;wpm&lt;/span&gt;            &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;18&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(download: &lt;a href=&quot;../assets/rb/eight-words-five-or-less-letters.rb.rb&quot;&gt;eight-words-five-or-less-letters.rb&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;words-having-size-between-2-and-4-letters-15-wpm&quot;&gt;2) 8 words having size between 2 and 4 letters (15 WPM)&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;# between-two-and-four.rb&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;require&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;cw&#39;&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nf&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;do&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;comment&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;8 words having size between 2 and 4 letters (15 WPM)&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;shuffle&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;wpm&lt;/span&gt;                 &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;15&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;no_shorter_than&lt;/span&gt;     &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;
